2) When we Want to Create a Copy of the Table Which we Have Already Created Use Below Query


A) CREATE TABLE student_latest as SELECT * FROM student;  [New Table Will be Created with All the details but Key Constaraint Nhi Rahege]

desc student_latest;

+-------------------------+-------------+------+-----+-------------------+-------------------+
| Field                   | Type        | Null | Key | Default           | Extra             |
+-------------------------+-------------+------+-----+-------------------+-------------------+
| student_id              | int         | NO   |     | 0                 |                   |
| student_fname           | varchar(30) | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
| student_lname           | varchar(30) | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
| student_mname           | varchar(30) | YES  |     | NULL              |                   |
| student_email           | varchar(30) | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
| student_phone           | varchar(15) | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
| student_alternate_phone | varchar(15) | YES  |     | NULL              |                   |
| enrollment_date         | timestamp   | NO   |     | CURRENT_TIMESTAMP | DEFAULT_GENERATED |
| selected_course         | int         | NO   |     | 1                 |                   |
| years_of_exp            | int         | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
| student_company         | varchar(30) | YES  |     | NULL              |                   |
| batch_date              | varchar(30) | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
| source_of_joining       | varchar(30) | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
| location                | varchar(30) | NO   |     | NULL              |                   |
+-------------------------+-------------+------+-----+-------------------+-------------------+





B) CREATE TABLE courses_latest as SELECT * FROM courses;  [New Table Will be Created with All the details but Key Constaraint Nhi Rahege]


desc courses_latest;

+-------------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field       | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+-------------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| course_id   | int         | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
| course_name | varchar(30) | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
| duration    | int         | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
| fees        | int         | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
+-------------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+




